      "content": "The techniques we apply are fine line. If you had some finger tattoos done by another artist that happened to stay, that doesn\u00e2\u0080\u0099t necessarily mean they will stay the same way again, so please don\u00e2\u0080\u0099t take that as a reference. There are many factors that affect the outcome, especially during the first 15 days of healing. If the tattoo holds well during those first 15 days, there\u00e2\u0080\u0099s a good chance it will last correctly for a long time.\n\nUnfortunately, we don\u00e2\u0080\u0099t currently have any flash available, as any flash designs we prepare usually sell out within a few days. However, if you have a reference or something you like, you can send us a photo and we can create something similar.",
